{"tid":361310,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我老母好ｏｎ９！！！","createTime":"2017-08-16T04:43:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-16T18:35:51.000Z","uid":431,"like":3,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c083147cdb6da2645244f8a5b47bab6432a750d3","tid":361310,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T04:43:25.000Z","msg":"我媽見超市結業，又買咗好多個杯麵返嚟，話抵喎。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n抵有撚用咩。。。垃圾食物！又肥又無營養。。。仲會食到塊面爛晒！仲要俾人咒罵！！！<br />\n上次我已經叫左佢唔好再買杯麵返嚟引誘我～<br />\n但佢死都唔聽，買咗一次（上一次買嘅俾晒親友攞咗返大陸～）又一次（今次又買多個返嚟！！）<br />\n成日話平就買返嚟俾我食，但佢就唔自己食！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\non9。。知唔知我塊面爛佢都有責任的？<br />\n如果佢唔係在我細個時整得太多煎炸嘢熱氣嘢我塊面本來都好靚的。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你可以話係我無自制力！但細路仔就係大人整乜佢就食乜㗎啦！<br />\n只要係好味就得，邊度識揀啲健康食物來食呢？<br />\n上次果鑊我就係日日食佢啲杯麵搞到唔為意自己塊面。。<br />\n無耐就成個下巴生晒暗瘡～<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依家謝咗但有好多印～我仲要搽藥膏ko返啲印佢！！！<br />\n今次佢買返嚟嘅杯麵我係一個都唔會食的！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唔想再爆暗瘡～我只能食啲清啲又健康嘅嘢（好似蒸魚同菜）<br />\n宣洩完～ｓｏｒｒｙ各位！！！我真係好想搵人申訴下先喺度開ｐｏｓｔ！！"},{"pid":"b93727b57502f4a3c480e4172dab752039b51f09","tid":361310,"uid":30678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T04:45:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com&d=MmY%2BrEgLL5rawwX1UuTFPRv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=a61856b7\" target=\"_blank\">www.facebook.com</a>"},{"pid":"b8aa6adbac6801189dcfb64373f221d15c38c975","tid":361310,"uid":431,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T04:47:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://www.facebook.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com&d=MmY%2BrEgLL5rawwX1UuTFPRv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=a61856b7\" target=\"_blank\">www.facebook.com</a></blockquote><br />\n咪撚柒啦。。。"},{"pid":"5ef85d2732bf7944d026b4